---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="About | C-Mind">
  <div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-stone-900 sm:text-4xl">About C-Mind</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-stone-600">
          Bridging the gap between technological potential and real-world care needs.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-4 border-l-4 border-teal-200 pl-6 h-full">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-8 text-stone-900">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-stone-600">
            C-Mind was created to address gaps in access, engagement, and continuity of mental health support by leveraging advances in artificial intelligence responsibly and ethically.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-4 border-l-4 border-teal-200 pl-6 h-full">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-8 text-stone-900">Our Approach</h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-stone-600">
            Our work is grounded in scientific evidence, implementation awareness, and real-world healthcare needs. We emphasize collaboration with clinicians, researchers, and care organizations to ensure appropriate deployment and impact.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center gap-8 text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-stone-50 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-stone-200"><span class="text-teal-600">→</span> Evidence-Based</div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-stone-50 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-stone-200"><span class="text-teal-600">→</span> Clinician-Aligned</div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-stone-50 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-stone-200"><span class="text-teal-600">→</span> Ethics-First</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
